data.description:
The sellers just dropped the price!! You don't want to miss this former model home with all the bells and whistles, on-trend colors and finishes just waiting for you. This 5 bedroom home has 4 bedrooms on the 2nd level with the 5th bedroom on the lower level. Awesome culdesac lot with finished walkout lower level, professional landscaping, expanded patio, irrigation system and black steel fencing. Custom stair gates and motorized blinds in the dining room and in the great room are some of the features the sellers have added. Walking distance to the community pool. Sellers have a VA assumable loan at an attractive rate that may be assumable for a buyer with VA entitlements (buyer must qualify and meet lender guidelines).
Sq ft, taxes and room dimensions are estimates, deemed reliable but not guaranteed.
